{"word":"G570 - ἀπιστία - apistía - ap-is-tee'-ah - Unbelief","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀπιστία</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>apistía"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>ap-is-tee'-ah"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Unbelief"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"அவிசுவாசம் - பெண்பால் பெயர்ச்சொல்"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"1. unfaithfulness, faithlessness"},{"paragraph":"2. lack of faith, unbelief"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Noun Feminine / பெயர்ச்சொல் (பெண்பால்)</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> From <a href=\"#/G571 - ἄπιστος - ápistos - ap'-is-tos/571\">G571</a>; <i>faithlessness</i>, that is, (negatively) <i>disbelief</i> (<i>want of</i> Christian <i>faith</i>), or (positively) <i>unfaithfulness</i> (<i>disobedience</i>): - unbelief."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G3640 - ὀλιγόπιστος - oligópistos - ol-ig-op'-is-tos/3640\">G3640</a>, <a href=\"#/G4100 - πιστεύω - pisteúō - pist-yoo'-o/4100\">G4100</a>, <a href=\"#/G4102 - πίστις - pístis - pis'-tis/4102\">G4102</a>, <a href=\"#/G4103 - πιστός - pistós - pis-tos'/4103\">G4103</a>, <a href=\"#/G4104 - πιστόω - pistóō - pis-to'-o/4104\">G4104</a>, <a href=\"#/G569 - ἀπιστέω - apistéō - ap-is-teh'-o/569\">G569</a>, <a href=\"#/G570 - ἀπιστία - apistía - ap-is-tee'-ah/570\">G570</a>, <a href=\"#/G571 - ἄπιστος - ápistos - ap'-is-tos/571\">G571</a>"}]}